name: 1927 (duchonic)
description:
• Start Level with 'Enter'
  • Restart Level with 'Esc'
  • Shoot with 'X'
  • Rocket with 'C'
  • Change view with 'W' up and 'S' down (rear with 'R')

Source code can be found here https://gitlab.com/duchonic/1927

It's all public domain. Use it, share it, learn it. It was my first project with godot and rust. Both relatively new to me so it was lot work learning the tools...
